@NODE Schietkram "Tja so isses halt"
@font helvetica.font 16


I needed a Hex-Converter, coz my old
program didn`t worked under OS3.1/3.x
and MC68060.
	
I tested all converters from the AmiNet
but the result wasn`t good enough for
me. I need to translate whole files to
HEX and not only one character...

So i used the TextLoader coz there where
already the parts what i needed...

After finished the HEX converter i founded
out that all other things are so easy and
i started with the rest...



@ENDNODE

