@NODE Prefs "Prefs"

Viewer     - Select a viewer program like CyberView,MultiView etc. 
ViewerPP   - It must be PPMore (PowerPacker format)
HELP       - Select the TextloaderNG.Guide (German or English)
Language   - Select the language from the TLNG/Locale directory
AGuide     - Select the path/program to view guides.
User_x     - Select a new rexx script, the selected file will be placed
             at the Rexxmenu...

After quitting the prefs the TLNG will reset to the new settings. 



@ENDNODE



@NODE Ochnö "Probleme Ochnöö..."

=======================================
@{bg highlight}      Not really Problems:      @{bg back}
=======================================

- Bug at Version 1! (AmiNet)
 
  goto @{" Last Changes !!! " Link err2} for more informations...

- EditorFont!!!

  If you can`t read the text or you can`t edit at the cursor
  position you selected an wrong font...

  Try fonts like: Topaz,XEN,XCourier,Clean,Thin611 etc. 
  
- Bug when running with HF-Math-Libs and the TLNG.Key!!!

  The TLNG.Key is not valid if you have installed this
  libs...

  I can`t stop this problem, coz the problem is the math.library
  it can`t count f.e. 200000000000-1!  


