  68060 (66 Mhz Blizzard & 128 MB 32-Bit Ram & 50 Mhz Cyberstorm & 32 MB &
         50 Mhz Cyberstorm & 128 MB 32-Bit Ram) Goil... 
    604 (240 MHZ) - Yep...

