@NODE Menu "Menü"

@{" Editormenu " }

Author                    - About us...
-------------------
Load...                   - Load a ASCII/FTXT Text...
Buffer                    - Change the Buffer to get more speed for the converter
@{" Text-Converter -> " Link Load1}
                          - Different Filters for documents 
                            goto: @{" Version Information " Link History} or @{" Features " Link Features}
Load as HEX...            - Load a file as HEX...
Load, Picture             - Show a picture... ***
Load Picture(PP)          - Dito
-------------------
Insert Text...            - Insert a text file
-------------------
@{" Save -> " Link Sav1}
Save BackUp               - Save a BackUp to RAM:
-------------------
Print                     - Print the document
-------------------
Quit                      - <-


@{" Text " }

Mark...                   - Mark a line at the cursorposition 
                            (You can also doubleclick onto the line. Use the Cursorkeys for
                             scrolling down or click once at the last line which you want to
                             select.)
Mark All...               - Mark the whole document
UnMark...                 - Unmark the text
Copy...                   - Copy the marked lines
Insert...                 - Insert the copied lines
Delete...                 - Delete/Cut marked lines (The deleted text is still at the buffer)
-------------------
Insert Newline            - <-
Insert paragraph          - <-
-------------------
Block ->                  - Like mark but it will mark the block to the next empty line.
-------------------
Cursor to Textend         - Cursor to the end of the document
Cursor to Textstart       - Cursor to the start of the document
-------------------
Clear Document            - <-
Delete line               - Delete a line at the cursor position
-------------------
UNDO                      - Brings back the last version of the document


@{" Special " }

Textfunctions ->
   Trim Text              - Delete the unused spaces
   Center text...         - <-
   Left...                - Text to the left
   Right...               - Text to the right
-------------------
Insert date              |  
Insert time              |- Insert Date/Time to the document 
Insert Date&Time         |
-------------------
Text uppercase            - <-
Text lowercase            - <-
Line uppercase            - <-
Line lowercase            - <-
-------------------
Convert to HEX...         - Change text to a HEX output
Convert to ASCII...       - Change the HEX-Text back to ASCII 
-------------------
Insert HTML code          - Insert a simple HTML code to the text
Remove HTML code          - Remove all HTML codes from the text...
-------------------
Crypt Text...             - This will crypt the document in unreadable format
Uncrtypt Text...          - This will uncrypt the text...
-------------------
Show Endmarks...          - Show the endposition of a line...


@{" Search " }

Search                    - Search for a word
Continue search           - This will continue the search for the given word
-------------------
Search&Replace            - Searches for a word and replace it with a new word

@{" Rexx " }              @{" More Info " Link f2}

Text to FinalWriter       - Send the text to FinalWriter
Text to PageLiner         - Send the text to PageLiner
Text to PageStream        - Send the Text to PageStream
Text to WordWorth         - Send the text to WordWorth 
-------------------
Text/GFX to PGS3          - Send (HTML) GFX/Text to PGS3
-------------------
User_1                    - Rexxport for you own modules,
User_2                      select Prefs to load your module
User_3                      to the menu...
User_4

!!!All programs accept Pageliner must be running!!!


@{" Preferences " }

Palette                   - Change the colors of Editorfont, Editorbackground etc.
Refresh                   - Refresh the TLNG mask.
Screenmode                - not finished yet! 
Buffer                    - Change the Buffer to get more speed for the converter
Set Editorfont            - Change the Editorfont to the font/size you want.
                            The Fontrequester will start proportional fonts only
                            first, to change this select the menuitem "only fixed
                            width" (off).
-------------------
Prefs...                  - Preferences to change the path/file for
                            locale,viewers,AmigaGuide and Rexxmodules.
                            
                            Following viewers tested: CyberShow,CyberWindow
                            IBrowse,AGuide,VT-Show

@{" OnlineHelp " }        
Start Help                - Start the Guide for the TLNG
-------------------
Icon Help                 - Switches off/on the icon help

@{" Statistic " }         

Document                  - Shows a statistic about the current document

Show Clock                - This will start the clock module. You can change it from
                            analog to digital.

SystemInfo                - Shows informations about your system...



@ENDNODE

