Version 1.11  25.02.99
----------------------------------------------

- RTF Filter

  This will strip the RTF code from the document...

- Fixed Replace error on Search&Replace

- Fixe SystemInfo for TextLoaderNG English/Deutsch 

Version 1.11a  02.03.99
----------------------------------------------

- Changed internal ClipBoards to Amiga Clipboards

  If you copy or cut a part (the whole) document,
  than you can use this with other programs which
  are also working with the clipboard device... 
  
  You also can insert clips from other programs.

  This is for registered users only -  for all 
  others users only the internal clips are working.
   
- Added Save to Clipboards to the menu:

  This will save the document to the Clipboards.
  You don`t must mark the text and select copy...

Version 1.12  13.03.99
----------------------------------------------

- Added Rexxport to the TLNG

  Send the text to FinalWriter,WordWorth,Pageliner
  and Pagestream3.

  All programs accept Pageliner must be running...

- Added UpperCase and LowerCase to the menu... 

Version 1.13  28.03.99
----------------------------------------------

- Fixed locale problem

  TLNG started only with the german locales...

