@NODE Filetypes "Filetypes"

Every character uses a HEX-Code f.e. $20 = Space, if you know 
this code you will be able to convert the file to a readable
file.

Some Programs like Word using a different code so i must give a
new value to it...

Other Programs like AmiWriter using nothing. 

WordWorth uses WTXT and a HEX value for a return...

etc.

------------------------------------------------------------------
  MORE FILTER COULD BE MADE !!!
  (I WILL NEED 2 DIFFERENT DOCUMENTS TO MAKE A NEW ONE...)
