=======================================
           ABOUT SHAREWARE
=======================================

DEMOVERSION
===========

The Demoversion is a Demoversion without
a working Key... (AHA!)

The only difference between the Fullversion 
and the Demoversion is, that the Demoversion
can`t SAVE...

t.m. if the Key is ok, than the DemoVersion
is no longer a DemoVersion than it`s a Full-
version...

And so i will call this version a Fulldemo-
version.

FREEVERSION
===========

Now it is a Fulldemonstrationfreeversion... Cool!



